@rhatdan Sure, I will work on it in the coming days!

@mtrmac Yeah, makes perfect sense. I still have some doubts, for example, about where I should declare the `userPolicyFile` variable. I guess that it makes a lot of sense to just declare it in the config files, example:

https://github.com/containers/podman/blob/cd58306a811b34c920479a933123b4ac9df0f614/vendor/github.com/containers/common/pkg/config/config_linux.go#L10-L20

However, I don't know if it's the best thing, nor I have a lot of experience with vendoring, so I would appreciate some pointers for this!
